About

This is a small python-based gyazo-like (http://gyazo.com) application for making screenshots of screen part. 
Originally written and tested under Ubuntu 11.10 x64.

Setup

Define variables and generate ssh keys:

$ ssh-keygen -t rsa
$ ssh server "mkdir .ssh; chmod 0700 .ssh"
$ scp .ssh/id_rsa.pub server:.ssh/authorized_keys2

Add scr command to command line:

$ cp scr ~/bin/scr
$ chmod +x ~/bin/scr
